## 16. WEBSOCKET EVENTS
A WebSocket connection is established at `wss://api.doc2id.ai/ws`. The client listens for:
*   `UPLOAD_PROGRESS`: Real-time bytes extracted from ZIP.
*   `GENERATION_PROGRESS`: Stream of `{ jobId, processed: 450, total: 1000 }`.
*   `JOB_COMPLETED`: Generation finished, triggers UI update.
*   `JOB_FAILED`: Generation halted due to fatal error.
*   `NEW_NOTIFICATION`: Triggers bell icon badge increment.

